&lt;h3 data-section-id=&quot;1mwc0up&quot; data-start=&quot;229&quot; data-end=&quot;255&quot;&gt;About Interstellar Lab&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;257&quot; data-end=&quot;537&quot;&gt;At &lt;span class=&quot;hover:entity-accent entity-underline inline cursor-pointer align-baseline&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;whitespace-normal&quot;&gt;Interstellar Lab&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;, our mission is to build a future full of life — on Earth and beyond. We believe in a world where technology enables humans to live in harmony with nature, where biodiversity thrives, and where terrestrial life becomes multi-planetary.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;539&quot; data-end=&quot;877&quot;&gt;To help build this future, we design, manufacture and operate controlled-environment biofarms that unlock the power of plants — both on Earth and in space. Our solutions combine hardware, AI and bioscience to recreate a wide range of environmental conditions, enabling plants, fungi and microorganisms to grow faster and more efficiently.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;879&quot; data-end=&quot;1216&quot;&gt;On Earth, we are pioneering molecular and bio-farming, increasing the production of nutrients, metabolites and bioactive compounds in plants while providing a sustainable and safe source of plant materials. Our customers include leading companies in the beauty, perfume, natural ingredients, food &amp;amp; beverage and nutraceutical industries.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1218&quot; data-end=&quot;1450&quot;&gt;To support space exploration, we also collaborate with space agencies and private companies to develop bio-farming units capable of producing food for astronauts and enabling research on the effects of microgravity on plant biology.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 data-section-id=&quot;1wct3r9&quot; data-start=&quot;1457&quot; data-end=&quot;1474&quot;&gt;About the Role&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1476&quot; data-end=&quot;1591&quot;&gt;We are looking for a Marketing &amp;amp; Communication Assistant to support our communication and marketing activities.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1593&quot; data-end=&quot;1917&quot;&gt;You will work closely with the Chief Communication Officer and assist with day-to-day tasks related to PR, media relations, social media and events. This position is ideal for a recent graduate or early-career professional looking to gain hands-on experience in communications within an innovative deep-tech company.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1919&quot; data-end=&quot;2110&quot;&gt;You are curious, organized and creative, with a strong interest in storytelling, media and digital communication. You enjoy learning, taking initiative and contributing to impactful projects.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 data-section-id=&quot;r8dte7&quot; data-start=&quot;2117&quot; data-end=&quot;2136&quot;&gt;Responsibilities&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 data-section-id=&quot;sio5d5&quot; data-start=&quot;2138&quot; data-end=&quot;2160&quot;&gt;PR &amp;amp; Media Support&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul data-start=&quot;2161&quot; data-end=&quot;2495&quot;&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1orxfcy&quot; data-start=&quot;2161&quot; data-end=&quot;2248&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;2163&quot; data-end=&quot;2248&quot;&gt;Assist in building and maintaining relationships with journalists and media outlets&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;19vjhal&quot; data-start=&quot;2249&quot; data-end=&quot;2310&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;2251&quot; data-end=&quot;2310&quot;&gt;Help manage and update the media and journalists database&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;894r3v&quot; data-start=&quot;2311&quot; data-end=&quot;2412&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;2313&quot; data-end=&quot;2412&quot;&gt;Support the preparation of press materials such as press releases, press kits and media briefings&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;n829v7&quot; data-start=&quot;2413&quot; data-end=&quot;2458&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;2415&q

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Mid-level Full Stack Developer&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;Full-time&lt;br&gt;In-person&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At Interstellar Lab, our mission is to build a future full of life, on Earth and beyond.&lt;br&gt;We believe in a world where technology enables humans to live in harmony with nature, where biodiversity thrives and expands, and where terrestrial life becomes multi-planetary.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;To build this future, we design autonomous biospheric systems to grow plants with precision, on Earth and in Space. Our AI-powered BioPods and BioCapsules leverage biosciences to reproduce and optimize growth conditions for a wide variety of high-value plants.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;On Earth, we pioneer molecular and biofarming, boosting the production of metabolites and bioactive compounds while offering sustainable, traceable, and high-quality natural ingredients to the beauty, fragrance, pharmaceutical, and nutraceutical industries.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In space, we collaborate with agencies and private companies to develop biofarming units that advance life science research in microgravity and lay the foundation for future biofactories in space, enabling innovative terrestrial applications and long-duration space missions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;As Mid-level Full Stack Developer at Interstellar Lab, you will design, build, and scale the digital backbone of our biospheric systems. You will develop backend and automation services, contribute to our React-based BioApp, and integrate emerging AI capabilities into our products. You will work closely with engineers, scientists, and designers to connect devices, data, and interfaces seamlessly.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and maintain backend services and APIs in Python (FastAPI)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contribute to frontend applications in React, ensuring smooth feature integration&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Connect sensors, devices, and automation layers across our digital ecosystem&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Integrate AI and agentic features to enhance functionality and autonomy&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure scalability, robustness, and reliability of digital infrastructures&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with engineers and designers on architecture and implementation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Write and maintain technical documentation and clean, maintainable code&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Test, troubleshoot, and iterate rapidly within a fast-paced environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Profile / Qualifications&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;3-6 years of experience in full-stack development&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficiency in Python (FastAPI) and modern backend frameworks&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Solid experience with React and frontend development principles&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Working knowledge of Docker and containerized environments&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with AWS or equivalent cloud platforms&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Interest in AI APIs, automation, and connected systems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong problem-solving and communication skills within multidisciplinary teams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fluent in English, French is a plus&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Equal Opportunity&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;Interstellar Lab is proud to be an equal opportunity employer. Interstellar Lab does not discriminate on the basis of race, regional color, national origin, gender (including pregnancy, childbirth, or related medical conditions), sexual orientation, gender identity, gender expression, age, status as a protected veteran, status as an individual with disability, or other applicable legally protected characteristics.&lt;/p&gt;

