&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Degree in mechanical, chemical, process, or environmental engineering&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;6+ years of experience in controlled environment systems, CEA, HVAC, or industrial fluid processes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong expertise in thermal engineering, fluid dynamics, and process control&lt;/li&gt;
